{"id":192,"date":"2025-02-02T17:01:06","date_gmt":"2025-02-02T14:01:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/?page_id=192"},"modified":"2025-02-24T16:26:43","modified_gmt":"2025-02-24T13:26:43","slug":"find-your-next-property-investment","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/find-your-next-property-investment\/","title":{"rendered":"Find your next property investment"},"content":{"rendered":"    <div class=\"top_section\">\r\n        <div class=\"top_container\">\r\n                        <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"top_elem elem_2\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/themes\/source\/images\/top_elem_2.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"top_wrap\">                <div class=\"top_info variable\">\r\n                    <div class=\"top_description\">                                        <h1 class=\"title_page light blur_anim\">Find your next property investment<\/h1>\r\n                                        <div class=\"top_text\">\r\n                        <p>We simplify property investing by finding the best opportunities in the UK and UAE, backed by expert research and exclusive market access.<\/p>\n       \r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"top_buttons\">\r\n                                                <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn\" href=\"https:\/\/meetings.hubspot.com\/josh-bullen\/first-call-booking?uuid=6cfb9071-b0ae-4628-b36e-f9c0ae58f7b2 \">Book a Call<\/a>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                        <\/div>                <\/div>\r\n                 \r\n                <\/div>            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"breadcrumbs p_big\">\r\n        <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <h3 class=\"title_category light\"><\/h3>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"solutions_section content_section\">\r\n                <div class=\"content_bg gradient reverse\">\r\n            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/solution_img_1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n        <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <div class=\"solution_inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"solution_description\">\r\n                                        <h2 class=\"title_big light\">Off-Plan<\/h2>\r\n                                        <div class=\"solution_description_text\">\r\n                        <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Secure the best properties in the most exciting developments before construction is complete and benefit from <strong>capital appreciation<\/strong> over the build cycle. <\/span><\/p>\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                    <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"solutions_section content_section\">\r\n                <div class=\"content_bg gradient reverse\">\r\n            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/C-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n        <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <div class=\"solution_inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"solution_description\">\r\n                                        <h2 class=\"title_big light\">Complete<\/h2>\r\n                                        <div class=\"solution_description_text\">\r\n                        <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Invest in new, complete, ready-to-rent properties, <strong>mitigating any risk<\/strong> of construction delays. <\/span><\/p>\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                    <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"solutions_section content_section\">\r\n                <div class=\"content_bg gradient reverse\">\r\n            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/D-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n        <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <div class=\"solution_inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"solution_description\">\r\n                                        <h2 class=\"title_big light\">Pre-tenanted<\/h2>\r\n                                        <div class=\"solution_description_text\">\r\n                        <p>Buy properties with tenants already in place, providing instant rental income. A great option for hands-off investors seeking <strong>cash flow from day one<\/strong>.<\/p>\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                    <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"solutions_section content_section\">\r\n                <div class=\"content_bg gradient reverse\">\r\n            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/E-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n        <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"container\">\r\n            <div class=\"solution_inner\">\r\n                <div class=\"solution_description\">\r\n                                        <h2 class=\"title_big light\">UAE<\/h2>\r\n                                        <div class=\"solution_description_text\">\r\n                        <p>Tap into one of the world\u2019s <strong>fastest-growing property markets<\/strong> with opportunities in Dubai and across the UAE. Benefit from strong yields, tax advantages, and world-class infrastructure.<\/p>\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                    <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"content_section bg_beige\">\r\n        <div class=\"content_container\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"container_inner\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"description_section w_900 m_100\">\r\n                                                <h2 class=\"title_section\">Finding top investments takes a lot of time and knowledge, many <em>don\u2019t know where to start\u2026<\/em><\/h2>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                                            <div class=\"point_triggers_wrap\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"point_trigger_item\">\r\n                            <div class=\"point_trigger_dot\"><\/div>\r\n                            <p class=\"point_trigger_text\"><strong>Too many options<\/strong> make it hard to know where to start or focus.<\/p>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"point_trigger_item\">\r\n                            <div class=\"point_trigger_dot\"><\/div>\r\n                            <p class=\"point_trigger_text\"><strong>Finding great deals<\/strong> is challenging without knowing where to look.<\/p>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"point_trigger_item\">\r\n                            <div class=\"point_trigger_dot\"><\/div>\r\n                            <p class=\"point_trigger_text\"><strong>Limited market knowledge<\/strong> leaves investors unsure how to identify or assess opportunities.<\/p>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                                        <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"content_section bg_light\">\r\n        <div class=\"content_container\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"container_inner\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"description_section\">\r\n                        <h2 class=\"title_section\">Your competitive <em>edge\u2026<\/em><\/h2>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"cards_wrap\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"card_item\">\r\n                            <div class=\"card_item_main\">\r\n                                                                <div class=\"card_item_icon\">\r\n                                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/card_icon_10.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                                <\/div>\r\n                                                                <p class=\"card_item_name\">Exclusive Market Access<\/p>\r\n                                                                <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                    <p>Leverage our <strong>trusted<\/strong> network of developers, agents and brokers across the UK & UAE for access to the best on and off-market opportunities. <\/p>\n                                <\/div>\r\n                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"card_item\">\r\n                            <div class=\"card_item_main\">\r\n                                                                <div class=\"card_item_icon\">\r\n                                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/card_icon_11.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                                <\/div>\r\n                                                                <p class=\"card_item_name\">We Do the Research<\/p>\r\n                                                                <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                    <p>We handpick the <strong>best<\/strong> opportunities and only share them with you after completing an extensive due diligence process. <\/p>\n                                <\/div>\r\n                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"card_item\">\r\n                            <div class=\"card_item_main\">\r\n                                                                <div class=\"card_item_icon\">\r\n                                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/card_icon_3.svg\" alt=\"\">\r\n                                <\/div>\r\n                                                                <p class=\"card_item_name\">Weekly Opportunities<\/p>\r\n                                                                <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                    <p>Receive our latest opportunities and deals, with weekly presentations that condense <strong>hours of research<\/strong> to help you make informed decisions efficiently.<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\r\n                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                                    <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"content_buttons mt_80\">\r\n                        <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn\" href=\"https:\/\/meetings.hubspot.com\/josh-bullen\/first-call-booking?uuid=6cfb9071-b0ae-4628-b36e-f9c0ae58f7b2\">Book a Call<\/a>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                    <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"content_section bg_dark\">\r\n        <div class=\"content_container\">                        <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"description_section\">\r\n                    <h3 class=\"title_category light\">How It Works<\/h3>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"triggers_wrap three_columns borders_none\">\r\n                                <div class=\"trigger_item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"trigger_item_inner\">\r\n                        <div class=\"trigger_item_circle\">1<\/div>\r\n                                                <p class=\"trigger_item_name\">Book a 15-min discovery call<\/p>\r\n                                                <div class=\"typical_text light\">\r\n                            <p>Our team will advise if Buy-to-Let is right for you. If it is, then we\u2019ll talk you through how to get started.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"trigger_item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"trigger_item_inner\">\r\n                        <div class=\"trigger_item_circle\">2<\/div>\r\n                                                <p class=\"trigger_item_name\">We'll get to work<\/p>\r\n                                                <div class=\"typical_text light\">\r\n                            <p>We\u2019ll make sure that you're set up correctly before recommending investment opportunities that are in line with your investment goals.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"trigger_item\">\r\n                    <div class=\"trigger_item_inner\">\r\n                        <div class=\"trigger_item_circle\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/trigger_check.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/div>\r\n                                                <p class=\"trigger_item_name\">Your portfolio is up and running<\/p>\r\n                                                <div class=\"typical_text light\">\r\n                            <p>We'll continue to keep you looped in on the latest opportunities, helping you build and manage your portfolio over time.<\/p>\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"content_buttons\">\r\n                    <a target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn\" href=\"https:\/\/meetings.hubspot.com\/josh-bullen\/first-call-booking?uuid=6cfb9071-b0ae-4628-b36e-f9c0ae58f7b2\">Book a Call<\/a>\r\n                <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n                    <\/div>    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"content_section bg_light\">\r\n        <div class=\"content_container\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"container_inner\">\r\n                                        <div class=\"description_section\">\r\n                        <h2 class=\"title_section\">Got Questions?<\/h2>\r\n                    <\/div>\r\n                                        <div class=\"faq_accordion accordion\">\r\n                                                <div class=\"faq_box accordion_box active\">\r\n                            <div class=\"faq_trigger accordion_trigger active\">\r\n                                <p class=\"faq_name\">How much money do I need to get started?<\/p>\r\n                                <div class=\"faq_plus\"><\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                            <div class=\"faq_container toggle_container\">\r\n                                <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To account for a deposit on an entry level property that we would recommend, plus acquisition fees (e.g. solicitors and government taxes), investors will need a minimum of \u00a370k.<\/span><\/p>\n                                <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"faq_box accordion_box active\">\r\n                            <div class=\"faq_trigger accordion_trigger\">\r\n                                <p class=\"faq_name\">How do we charge for our services?<\/p>\r\n                                <div class=\"faq_plus\"><\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                            <div class=\"faq_container toggle_container\">\r\n                                <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our fees are typically covered by the seller and so we do not charge buyers for access to our investments and helping you through the acquisition process. For some specific off-market opportunities, our fees aren\u2019t always covered and so we will charge a small sourcing &amp; acquisition fee that we will make you aware of from the start. <\/span><\/p>\n                                <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"faq_box accordion_box active\">\r\n                            <div class=\"faq_trigger accordion_trigger\">\r\n                                <p class=\"faq_name\">What levels of returns can I expect?<\/p>\r\n                                <div class=\"faq_plus\"><\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                            <div class=\"faq_container toggle_container\">\r\n                                <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Returns vary depending on a number of factors, such as; location, type of property, whether using financing or not as well as how you calculate it \u2013 e.g. Net vs Gross return, whether or not you factor in capital appreciation, however our team will always provide a full financial breakdown for each individual project, talking you through the level of returns you can expect and what is factored in. <\/span><\/p>\n                                <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                                <div class=\"faq_box accordion_box active\">\r\n                            <div class=\"faq_trigger accordion_trigger\">\r\n                                <p class=\"faq_name\">What sort of property do you invest in?<\/p>\r\n                                <div class=\"faq_plus\"><\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                            <div class=\"faq_container toggle_container\">\r\n                                <div class=\"typical_text\">\r\n                                    <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We focus on giving our clients access to the best opportunities and so we don\u2019t restrict ourselves to any one particular type of property, however we will always have a flight to quality approach, only showing our clients properties that will perform well over the long term. <\/span><\/p>\n                                <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <\/div>\r\n            <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n    <\/div>\r\n\n\n    <div class=\"cta_section content_section\">\r\n                <div class=\"content_bg\">\r\n            <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/sourceinvestments.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/B.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n        <\/div>\r\n                <div class=\"content_container p_120\">\r\n            <div class=\"container\">\r\n                <div class=\"cta_info\">\r\n                                        <h3 class=\"title_category light\">Next Steps<\/h3>\r\n                                        <h2 class=\"title_section light\">Read